						<summary>

						<p>Records the gift of 1(1/2) <hi rend="italic">mā</hi> of land in <hi rend="italic">Tirukkuṟaippaṟṟu</hi> as <hi rend="italic">Jīvaṉaśēsham</hi> to Eḍuttakai-Aḻagiyāṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Tirukkuṟuṅguḍi-Nambi by Mārattammaṉ, in the service of <hi rend="bold">Bōgaya Daṇḍanāyaka</hi> (vide No. 157 below), for supplying a flower garland every day for the merit of the latter. The record is dated in the <hi rend="bold">21st year</hi> of the king.</p>						

						</summary>
